"""

Multiple Choice Options are:

(a) new_lease = signature + lease

(b) new_lease = f'{lease} + {signature}'

(c) new_lease = lease + signature

(d) new_lease = f'''

Dear Dot, 

This document validates that you are beholden to a monthly payment of rent for this house.

Rent is to be paid by the first of every month.

Fill in your signature to agree to these terms.

-------------

Please Sign Here: {signature} 

'''

(e) new_lease = f'{lease} {signature}'

(d) If you try entering each in the console, you'll see that (d) is the only option that lets the signature appear immediately after "Please Sign Here:" on the same line and not on the following line.
"""

new_lease = f'''

Dear Dot, 

This document validates that you are beholden to a monthly payment of rent for this house.

Rent is to be paid by the first of every month.

Fill in your signature to agree to these terms.

-------------

Please Sign Here: {signature} 

'''
